Task 5
Create two groups: developers and qa. Verify both groups were successfully created and display the complete list of groups on the system.
------Group creation-------
sudo groupadd developers
sudo groupadd qa

--------group verification-----
getent group developers
getent group qa

---------all list------
cat /etc/group

